Class DomainObject

java.lang.Object
CSC540.WolfWR.models.DomainObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Discount, Discount.DiscountID, Member, Merchandise, SignUp, Staff, Store, Supplier, Transaction, TransactionItem, TransactionItemID
public abstract class DomainObject extends Object implements Serializable
This is an abstract base class for domain objects in the application. It implements Serializable to allow objects of subclasses to be serialized, making them suitable for persistence mechanisms such as database storage or session management.

The DomainObject class serves as a common superclass for all entities in the application.
